Alias Generator

usage: aliasgen.py [-h] --path PATH [--destination DESTINATION] [--console]
                   [--levels LEVELS] [--text-editor TEXT_EDITOR]
                   [--media-editor MEDIA_EDITOR]

Generate path and file bash and zhrc compatible aliases from a specific path.

  -h, --help                    show this help message and exit
  --path PATH                   Path to target
  --destination DESTINATION     Generate file with aliases
  --console                     Print aliases statements to the console
  --levels LEVELS               Maximum paths to transverse
  --text-editor TEXT_EDITOR     Set text editor
  --media-editor MEDIA_EDITOR   Set media editor